[While an effort to control the news and the data is not unexpected, it
unfortunately has an immediate result in feeding a widening perception of
lack of transparency. This can engender both doubt and suspicion of the
reliability of any figures produced, and then even of competence. The
sooner this is corrected the better. - Mod.MHJ
